 -------------------------------------------------------------------------------
               LegSem LegStar Schemagen Eclipse plugin Version 1.1.0
                                   Release Notes
 -------------------------------------------------------------------------------

PREREQUISITES:

 This plugin requires Eclipse 3.2.1. It uses the XML Schema Generator module which in
 turn relies on Ant.
 
 You must install the XML Schema Generator module before you can use this Eclipse plugin.
 
 The XML Schema Generator module can be downloaded from {{{../legstar-schemagen/download.html} here}}.
 
 The XML Schema Generator Eclipse Plugin also requires the LegStar Common Eclipse plugin. For
 intructions on how to install the Common Eclipse Plugin,
  see {{{../legstar-common-plugin/release-notes.html} here}}.
 
INSTALLING/UNINSTALLING:

 [[1]] Ensure that the base XML Schema Generator module has been installed and that the folder
  holding native libraries has been added to the search PATH.
    
 [[2]] Within Eclipse, create a remote site using:
 
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  Help-->Software Updates-->Find and Install-->Search for new features-->New Remote site.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  
  Have the URL point to http://www.legsem.com/legstar/eclipse/update and select the
    XML Schema Generator feature.

 [[3]] Restart Eclipse and check that "LegsStar Schema Generator" shows up in:
 
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  Help-->About Eclipse SDK-->Plug-in details.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   
 [[4]] Start the plugin from the LegStar menu or the toolbar button.
   
 [[5]] To uninstall, use:

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  Help-->Software Updates-->Manage Configurations.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

  then right-click on the feature you wish to uninstall.

